%% Omni Architect | Feature: F001 - Authentication | Stories: US001, US002
sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Usuário
    participant F as Frontend
    participant A as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant DB as Database

    U->>F: Informa email e senha
    F->>A: POST /auth/login
    A->>Auth: Validar credenciais
    Auth->>DB: Buscar usuário por email
    DB-->>Auth: Dados do usuário
    Auth->>Auth: Verificar hash da senha
    Auth-->>A: JWT + Refresh Token
    A-->>F: 200 OK { token, refreshToken }
    F-->>U: Redirecionado ao dashboard